{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">2-Player Cooperative Gameplay:</h2>Work together with a friend to fix the plumbing. Each player has a unique role, requiring coordination and teamwork to succeed.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775170/extras/gif1.gif?t=1730837641\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Time-Attack Challenges:</h2>Race against the clock to connect pipes before the water leaks out. The pressure is high, and mistakes can lead to disastrous consequences.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775170/extras/gif2.gif?t=1730837641\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Asymmetrical Co-op Mechanics:</h2>Each character has specific tasks that cannot be completed alone. M\u00e1rcio rotates the pipes while Luiz carries them. You'll need to rely on your partner to complete your own objectives.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775170/extras/gif3.gif?t=1730837641\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Player vs. Environment:</h2>Face off against the environment as you navigate through the dark, monstrous world of Hallowville, filled with peculiar and terrifying characters.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775170/extras/gif4.gif?t=1730837641\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Art Style:</h2>A blend of 1980s newspaper cutouts, TV news aesthetics, and a mix of 2D and 3D elements create a visually distinct experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2775170/extras/gif5.gif?t=1730837641\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unexpected Narrative Twists:</h2>Uncover the twisted and bloody secrets of Hallowville as you progress through the game, revealing that not everything is as it appears.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s